### Response Fields

#### `success` (boolean)
- `true`: Import completed (may have had failures)
- `false`: Fatal error occurred

#### `message` (string)
- Human-readable summary of import result

#### `summary` (object)
```typescript
{
  totalRows: number,           // Total rows in input
  successfulImports: number,   // Rows successfully imported
  failedRows: Array<{
    success: false,
    rowIndex: number,          // 1-based row number
    reason: string             // Why the row failed
  }>,
  created: {
    parts: number,             // New parts created
    rejectionTypes: number,    // New rejection types created
    reworkTypes: number,       // New rework types created
    zones: number              // New zones created
  },
  warnings: string[]           // Any warnings (e.g., dry-run message)
}
```

#### `logs` (string[])
Array of detailed operation logs for debugging:
- `[IMPORT] [DEBUG]` - Detailed operations
- `[IMPORT] [INFO]` - Important operations (creating entities, etc.)
- `[IMPORT] [WARN]` - Warnings (row skipped, etc.)
- `[IMPORT] [ERROR]` - Errors (processing failed, etc.)

